wikipedia_page.main: Agnes Elizabeth Jenns (January 1911 – 11 January 1968) was a 1930s British film actress.Jenns married actor Harry Crocker in late 1936 and then Gardner Clarence Carpenter in late 1939.  She made her American film debut in A Star Is Born, acting alongside Fredric March and Janet Gaynor.She died on January 11, 1968, Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin, United States.
